{"tid":2372831,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美情報總監提名人選：對華採取積極進取立場","createTime":"2021-01-20T04:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T08:34:02.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"396e5e3b0a47c8d7318b37a7b9c90703bea50d5b","tid":2372831,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"美情報總監提名人選：對華採取積極進取立場<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571303-20210120.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571303-20210120.htm&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmek6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=59e7f47e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571303-20210120.htm&h=ba10c955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571303-20210120.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n獲美國候任總統拜登提名出任國家情報總監的海恩斯說，支持對中國採取積極進取立場。<br />\n<br />\n在參議院情報委員會的確認提名聽證會上，海恩斯說，上任後的首要工作，包括恢復情報界的信任和信心，以及重建美國人民對情報界的信任和信心。她又說，面對中國的好鬥和強勢獨斷，美國的政策要不斷演變，她會運用更多資源，應對中國的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n曾任中情局副局長和白宮幕僚的海恩斯也表示，伊朗距離恢復嚴格遵守核協議仍很遙遠，如果伊朗嚴格遵守，拜登政府可能也會重返核協議。"},{"pid":"9c633deb8fdc283948475dcd36c005df97926057","tid":2372831,"uid":58841,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:22:45.000Z","msg":"如果伊朗嚴格遵守，拜登政府可能也會重返核協議。<br />\n<br />\n笑到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n積極進取=養到支那肥肥白白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6308cf01034fc0b3ca3bbe08c835d34532eb5fb","tid":2372831,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T05:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b205fffe58dacd2f55da5bcc0ce7956ab225e64","tid":2372831,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2