和信心。她又說，面對中國的好鬥和強勢獨斷，美國的政策要不斷演變，她會運用更多資源，應對中國的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n曾任中情局副局長和白宮幕僚的海恩斯也表示，伊朗距離恢復嚴格遵守核協議仍很遙遠，如果伊朗嚴格遵守，拜登政府可能也會重返核協議。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:09:37.000Z","msg":"直接係中共到請人，攪掂"},{"pid":"1a8bffc10ba8306e5d5c8d8a364741556415ac28","tid":2372831,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06c6c70012075459be6c6bbbdf7c3a1a543b7000","tid":2372831,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:41:22.000Z","msg":"沈旭暉話當拜登政府發現傳統手段冇效，就會迫住行返侵侵路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:14:28.000Z","msg":"佢真係一個象牙塔學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本唔會有所謂有效丶冇效，對民主黨政府來講，只會有幾多來自支那嘅着數"},{"pid":"ef150301f267331f2c13b1aea78899c8a9b475a1","tid":2372831,"uid":35457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a8bffc10ba8306e5d5c8d8a364741556415ac28","tid":2372831,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06c6c70012075459be6c6bbbdf7c3a1a543b7000","tid":2372831,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:41:22.000Z","msg":"沈旭暉話當拜登政府發現傳統手段冇效，就會迫住行返侵侵路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:14:28.000Z","msg":"佢真係一個象牙塔學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本唔會有所謂有效丶冇效，對民主黨政府來講，只會有幾多來自支那嘅着數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:19:15.000Z","msg":"如果佢係象牙塔學者<br />\n你係咪鍵盤鬥士？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3620752f336f5e56198352b0124b4a7c1d03d47","tid":2372831,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06c6c70012075459be6c6bbbdf7c3a1a543b7000","tid":2372831,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:41:22.000Z","msg":"沈旭暉話當拜登政府發現傳統手段冇效，就會迫住行返侵侵路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:34:02.000Z","msg":"放